    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and chassis balance the chassis is known for. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight tolerances, offering a visceral, analog performance experience.",
