    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i M-Sport in Mediterranean Blue Metallic. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor road wear consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the Mocha Nappa leather seats are supple and free of tears, complemented by Fineline Cove wood trim. Every feature, from the Harman Kardon surround sound system to the gesture-controlled infotainment, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it has received regular synthetic oil changes and recently had a full brake service. It drives with the smooth, assertive power you expect from a turbocharged inline-six. Complete with a full service history and two sets of keys, this sedan offers a premium driving experience that balances luxury with reliable performance.",
